('90903','31301','5','Finca  with guest house'),
('90904','31302','5','This beautiful Finca is situated on a quiet, about 26,000 square flat plot on the outskirts  of wine-village\r\nThe idyllic finca-style villa was renovated about 7 years ago and is in top condition.\r\nThe approximately 870m ² of living space spread over 3 floors.\r\nThe ground floor is an entrance hall, guest WC, living room, TV room, dining room, 2 bedrooms each with a bathroom en suite and a country kitchen with cooking island and dining table.\r\nOn the 1st floor are the master bedroom with dressing room, an office room (children''s room)  a spacious bathroom and a terrace. On this floor there is another bedroom with bathroom.\r\nOn the 2nd floor is a large bedroom with en suite bathroom and a terrace. In the so-called tower room is an office space.\r\nThe separate guest house are an apartment with living-dining room - kitchen, a bedroom and a bathroom as well as separate guest bedroom with bathroom.\r\nThe center of the park-like garden is the 20 x 6m large swimming pool surrounded by a chill-out terrace and a covered barbecue. Children can play on the playground covered wit a sun sail or on the artificial turf football field.\r\nThe high-quality interior equipment includes, inter alia, a solar assisted under floor heating on the ground level, air conditioning, double glazed wooden windows, Corradi Kitchen stove and -fridge, fireplace , panic doors in the main bedrooms and much more.\r\n5 garages provides ample space for Dad''s toys.\r\nThis unique property is ideal for families with children and for year round use.\r\n'),
